Package: pdes
Type: Package
Title: Numerical solvers for parabolic PDEs, PIDEs and HJB-PDEs
Version: 0.1.0
Author: S. Hill
Maintainer: S. Hill <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: Solvers via Monte-Carlo, finite difference, and analytic solutions
    for parabolic PDE/PIDEs arising from Feynman-Kac or Fokker-Planck problems.
    Also provided are solvers for HJB-PDEs arising from stochastic control problems.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
